>Every time i try to log in to the admin, it tells me I have the wrong password. I went to PHP admin and changed manually the password :but no luck, still &#8220;wrong password&#8221;.</p>\n<p>When I have W3TC activated : login page error is &#8220;wrong password&#8221;<br />\nWhen I have W3TC deleted from server/deactivated : login page error is &#8220;wrong password fot XXXX username. Reset password?&#8221;<br />\nI did the reset password, received the email, changed it, but still no luck.<br />\nI forgot to say that I deactivated W3TC manually from the server following the dozens of tuto I found for this on the internet, so I did it well (deleting the right files/folders and lines in wp-config, htaccess&#8230;), I deleted/renamed everything that is necessary to delete W3TC, but no luck after this.</p>\n<p>I had Wordfence activated, so deactivated it.<br />\nI deactivated all plugins, themes, but no luck.<br />\nWordpress + Woocommerce were up to date.<br />\nI can&#8217;t think of anything I haven&#8217;t tried to do.</p>\n<p>My problem is : I can&#8217;t access my dashboard anymore after a clear cache !</p>\n<p>Please help me  I have tried everything for the past 24 hours!<br />\nThanks</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/SjgV9XR7y8E\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"eminems\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/cant-access-dashboard-after-clear-cache/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:16;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8: